      "title": "ElizaOS Community Discussion and Builder Activity - May 31, 2026",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Community members exchanged greetings throughout the day in the general discussion channel. A notable introduction came from Faouzi, founder of Arsenal Quant, who is building the Arsenal Decision Engine, described as a high-performance decision oracle for DeFi agents. The project integrates with elizaOS via MCP and uses L402 Lightning for payments. Faouzi expressed enthusiasm about connecting with other builders in the DeFAI space.",
