        },
        {
          "text": "In the coders channel, Odilitime flagged an issue for Stan to investigate, and Stan acknowledged it and indicated he would look into it. Separately, a community member posted a paid opportunity seeking a reliable partner for simple operational tasks and business relationship management. The role requires a native English speaker with clear communication skills, the ability to participate in client meetings, and a preference for stable income. The position is listed as remote and is open only to residents of the US, Canada, and UAE, with no technical experience or degree required.",
